<title>A THIANG THITUMNAK CH465</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A thiang thit-umnak hmaizah pek in kan tuah, Kan Bawipa nih a chimtak
 cang, Vawlei thawh ka in Bawipa nih a ser cang, Nu le va pumkhat si awkah.

[C1]
   Maw dawtnak Bawipa, hi thit-umnak thiang cu, Fehter law thluachuah
   pe ko. An i dawtnak thukpi ah hram thla dingin, Thiang thlarau in lam run
   hruai hna.

[V2]
 Kheng khamtu um lo, a thiangmi thit-umnak, Khrihfa mi kan nun can a
 si, Bawipa dawtnak chungah thit-umnak hmun seh, Khrihfa chungkhar tha si
 dingin.

[C2]
   Maw dawtnak Bawipa, hi thit-umnak thiang cu, Fehter law thluachuah
   pe ko. An i dawtnak thukpi ah hram thla dingin, Thiang thlarau in lam run
   hruai hna.

[V3]
 Pathian komhmi cu mi nih 'hen hna hlah u, Dawn-khantu thil vialte lo
 seh, Thleidan le nautat nak lungthin lo dih seh, Thluachuah vanni za um
 seh ti'n.

[C3]
   Maw dawtnak Bawipa, hi thit-umnak thiang cu, Fehter law thluachuah
   pe ko. An i dawtnak thukpi ah hram thla dingin, Thiang thlarau in lam run
   hruai hna.</lyrics>
</song>